Signature Global Real Estate says it has collaborated with Sobha Realty of Dubai, UAE, to launch the project ‘Buy a Part of Dubai’ on May 30, 2022 in Lagos. According to a statement by the company, the event would hold at The George Hotel, 30 Lugard Avenue, Ikoyi. The statement said benefits for participants would include full insight into investment in Dubai. The event is also expected to unfurl vital facts such as eligibility to obtain a golden visa, Dubai Hospitality Package and the Zero Tax Investment Opportunity. It added that participants would be eligible for free fee consultancy service from one of Dubai’s top real estate consultants.  All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com